Upgrade
=======

Make sure you are using the latest version, as
[[upgrading|doc/upgrade]] might solve your problem.

Check if the problem is already known
=====================================

You can have a look at:

  - The [[list of known issues|support/known_issues]]
  - The [list of things that will be in the next release](https://redmine.tails.boum.org/code/projects/tails/issues?query_id=327)
  - The [[!tails_redmine desc="rest of our open tickets on Redmine"]]

